quran[12]{c,v,t}:
  18,71,"Basi ni ŵaŵigwile ŵanaŵaŵili (Khidr ni Musa achijendaga mungulugulu mbwani), mpaka pandema jaŵakwesile m’chombo; (Khidr) jwachipowele. (Musa) jwatite: “Ana nchipowele (chombochi) kuti mwamisye achimisyene? Chisimu pamasile pantesile chindu chekulungwa changalumbana.”"
  18,72,"(Khidr) jwatite: “Ana nganimbecheta yanti chisimu mmwejo nganim’ba nkombwele kupilila none?”"
  18,73,"(Musa) jwatite: “Nkamba ilagasyo ligongo lyakuliŵalila kwangu, soni ngasimunganganika ni isausyo yekulungwa nnope pa chisako changu (chakusa kunkuya mmwe).”"
  18,74,"Basi ni ŵajendelechele ŵanaŵaŵili (pa ulendo wao panyuma pakutuluka m’chombo mula), mpaka pandema jaŵakasimene kanchanda; basi (Khidr) ŵakauleje. (Musa) jwatite: “Ana m’buleje mundu jwangali chaleŵile, jwanganaulaga mundu? Chisimu pamasile pantesile chindu chakunyalaya kusyene.”"
  18,75,"(Khidr) jwatite: “Ana nganinansalila yanti chisimu mmwejo nganim’ba nkombwele kupilila none?”"
  18,76,"(Musa) jwatite: “Naga nam’busye yachindu chine panyuma pachalakwechi, basi ngasimungunda soni kulongana namwe, pamasile pampochele usulu wakwanila kuumila kukwangu.”"
  18,77,"Basi ni ŵajendelechele ŵanaŵaŵili (pa ulendo wao), mpaka pandema jaŵaichilile ŵandu ŵa m’musi (wa Antwâkia), ŵaŵendile yakulya achimisyene musio, nambo ŵakanile kwakalibuchisya. Basi ni ŵalisimene mwalakwemo lipupa linankusaka kugwa, basi (Khidr) ni jwalijimiche. (Musa) jwatite: “Nkasache, chisimu chene nkagapochelele malipilo (masengo galakwega nitukaasuumiile yakulya).”"
  18,78,"(Khidr) jwatite: “Aku ni kulekangana kwa chilikati cha une nomwe. Sano chinantagulile ngopolelo sya ichindu yanganinkombola kuipililila ata panandi.”"
  18,79,"“Sano chombochila, basi chaliji chaŵandu ŵakulaga ŵakamula masengo m’mbwani, ninasachile kuti nachipe ayibu, sano paujo pao paliji pana mwenye juŵaliji nkujigala chombo chilichose (chambone) mwakotosya.”"
  18,80,"“Sano kanchanda kala, nikuti achinangolo ŵakwe ŵaliji ŵakulupilila, basi nitwajogwepe kuti atakwakanganichisya kutenda yakusumba mpika ni yaukafili.”"
  18,81,“Nitwasachile kuti Ambuje ŵao ŵatindanichisye ni jwambone kumpunda jwele pakutakata ni jwakuŵandichila nnope ku chanasa (chakwatendela achinangolo ŵakwe).”
  18,82,"“Sano lipupa lila, nilyaliji lya ŵanache ŵaŵili ŵawina mu nsindamo; sano pasi pakwe paliji pana chipanje chao (chaŵasalachisye malemu baba ŵao); sano baba ŵao ŵaliji ntenda ngoto. Basi Ambuje ŵenu niŵasachile kuti akuyiche ŵanaŵaŵilio komangala kwao, mwanti chalikopochesye chipanje chaocho, (awu) kuŵa ukoto wakuumila kwa Ambuje ŵenu. Ni nganindenda yalakweyi mwaulamusi ŵangu. Asi ni ngopolelo sya ichindu yanganinkombola kuipililila.”"